author: Conor Lally
title: Woman found dead in Kilkenny house after gardaí trace phone call
description: Pensioner may have been dead in house since last weekend
content:
A pensioner was found murdered in Kilkenny after a man contacted gardaí by telephone and claimed a woman had been killed in the city.
